          <text>
            <![CDATA[ <p><b>Small Business Administration Franchise Loan Transparency Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires a franchisor seeking&nbsp;guaranteed lending from the Small Business Administration to disclose historical revenue and store-closure information to any prospective franchisee before the loan will be approved.</p>]]>
          </text>
